--     orgs (demo, kkn, thaisummit, etc.) that are absent from the active allowlist.
--   - Deletes cascade to user_organizations, organization_invitations, support_* rows.
--   - organization_trial_requests.organization_id is set to NULL (ON DELETE SET NULL).
